These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different games are played: go, mah-jongg
1. the person playing go is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | go |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, blue
1. the person who likes blue is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |
| Color   | red | blue |

 #################################

 
